First off, I'd like to apologize to Iron Raptor for taking so long. Sorry, 
thanx for bugging me about this, IR!

::Prowl::

The door to the CR chamber opens, Prowl stepping out and looking around. He 
sees Iron Raptor, surprized that she wasn't somewhere off on buisness.

"What's going on, love?" he asks, walking up to her and trying to slide his 
arms around her, not sure if she was over the truck thing yet. But she was 
the femmbot he loved, and he would keep trying.
